&lt;p&gt;The right person will combine deep relationships in K-12 education, technical fluency with LLMs, and the entrepreneurial drive to build something new at the frontier of AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This role is distinct from our Account Executive function: while AEs drive scaled adoption of Anthropic&#39;s core products, Program Managers build deep partnerships that require custom deployments, research collaboration, and hands-on program design. You&#39;ll work with a smaller portfolio of flagship partners where the goal is driving impact metrics and creating learnings that benefit the broader ecosystem.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
